          "description": "A bit slow in refilling some medications and terrible in transferring prescriptions to other pharmacies. Beware that they usually close earlier than what they say on the door.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JMGIzRnBha2xtVFhaYWJGaEdlVXQ0VjJGRU1YYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xf3c26961bafdbc40!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmI0b3FpaklmTXZabFhGeUt4V2FEMXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
