          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdvRM38sZt9tpg4_a-V9jHQCCDp8T6DC1bwM8gG4FIBC2v2YtU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Please note that this pharmacy is successfuly taking down negative reviews. I guess that's a service you can buy from Google.\n\nMy original negative review (along with the dozens of others that were previously here), speak to the incredible rudeness of the pharmacy manager.\n\nThese are THE WORST, absolutely incompetent pharmacy staff in the city and that says volumes. Instead of ordering new stock of medicine, they wait for the customer to call them days later before attempting to order the meds. And they WILL make you wait at least two hours despite there being only three people in line ahead of you on the phone. And they WILL hang up on you not once, not twice, but three times. Absolute garbage staff at an absolutely garbage pharmacy.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNuczdXUjFBRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xf3c26961bafdbc40!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICns7WR1AE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "Edited 2 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-04-24T22:55:34+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Marley Jaeger",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "101884696990188533176",
          "user_review_count": 1,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIP0YmkhofD7aNVGkg82HSeSLoqrTl0hK6Qa-YupbFCMDEaO1k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Person on the phone in the pharmacy was so rude and condescending today. Have called a dozen other pharmacies asking the same questions related to the ADHD medication shortage, and no where else has given me any difficulty. I\u2019m just trying to get my meds in a really hard time to get them- I don\u2019t need to be catching strays on the phone with the pharmacy! :(",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN2dWUtUU9nEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0xf3c26961bafdbc40!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICvue-QOg%7C%7C?hl=en",
