          "description": "I am changing to a farther-away pharmacy because I am so tired of dealing with this one. Wait times are incredibly long even when it is not busy. The pharmacists often insist I have no prescriptions available until I pull up the app and show them I do. This back and forth has taken up to 45 minutes before.",
